cards.markdown: [![From the Queue: Wing Mirror](https://i1.wp.com/www.onemanandhisblog.com/content/images/2006/07/ftqmain-tm.jpg?resize=420%2C316 "From the Queue: Wing Mirror")](https://i0.wp.com/www.onemanandhisblog.com/content/images/2006/07/ftqmain.jpg) Been a little while since I did a gratuitous photo project, so here’s one from Friday. Thanks to a screw-up on the M25, I spent loads of time queueing on the A25, so I took the opportunity to get a few unusual grabs.
